{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"481b50cdbb","title":"开第三师后相机解决东明之敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fed18b3df3","index":0,"year":1946,"month":9,"day":5,"articleId":"481b50cdbb"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6114858a29","type":"paragraph","text":"开第三师后相机解决东明之敌口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"481b50cdbb"},{"id":"bd12748e11","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年9月5日）刘、邓：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"481b50cdbb"},{"id":"c1bd24f2e9","type":"paragraph","text":"现向前后王楼、砖庙集进攻之川军两个旅（一二二及一二七）不甚疲劳，且两旅靠拢，似较难打。现向东明进攻之川军两个团，是两个师的部队（三一一团属四十一师，三七四团属四十七师），经过鄂北、陕南长途酸涉，比较疲劳，且远离其后梯队，孤军深入，直迫东明城下，似较好打。望以一部固守东明，待第三师完全解决后，相机解决东明附近之敌。请按实情决定","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"481b50cdbb"},{"id":"beb6a576bb","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"481b50cdbb"},{"id":"d48f9c2da8","type":"paragraph","text":"申微子[I]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给普冀鲁豫野战军司令员刘伯承","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"481b50cdbb"}],"page":{"id":"c947f6f90d","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"481b50cdbb","start":132,"end":132}}}},"__N_SSG":true}